|------|--------|
| [parse_at.sh](file:///d:/Projects/QM%20PROJECT/QManager/scripts/usr/lib/qmanager/parse_at.sh) | Discount first NR SCC in NSA mode |
| [events.sh](file:///d:/Projects/QM%20PROJECT/QManager/scripts/usr/lib/qmanager/events.sh) | No change needed (math self-corrects) |
| [cell-data.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/QM%20PROJECT/QManager/components/cellular/cell-data.tsx) | Already fixed (now also defended by backend) |

## Verification

With the backend fix, the JSON will output:
```json
"nr_ca_active": false,
"nr_ca_count": 0
```
Instead of the current incorrect `nr_ca_active: true, nr_ca_count: 1`.
